{"tid":2116904,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔比Home office仲要人夾錢送禮比老細","createTime":"2020-07-20T12:40:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-21T01:07:44.000Z","uid":327552,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d178345f024b913fd898e801110cfd99c03c31be","tid":2116904,"uid":327552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T12:40:10.000Z","msg":"本身要夾錢送禮比CEO都算鳩數，當豪比狗。<br />\n但宜家疫情爆撚到咁都唔撚比人wfh ，條氣真係唔撚順，如果唔係今日個個都逼住夾錢，真係唔柒想比埋一份。<br />\n<br />\n屌你老未臭閪，番工仲要逼鳩埋員工夾錢籌旗送禮比你肉唔肉鳩酸d? <br />\n<br />\n仲好意思話上市，如果唔係疫情，洗鬼逼住留係你間閪公司做咁耐，走撚佐十世啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qaY77KG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqaY77KG.jpg&h=a488145d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"59e243f3cb5fd3d8fcd4f5d11399335ec23f6ec9","tid":2116904,"uid":60635,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T12:42:20.000Z","msg":"40點買LV外套？<br />\n幾百個人夾？"},{"pid":"080ca6221c353129c607df4d55ed68a079593ddd","tid":2116904,"uid":290083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T12:42:25.000Z","msg":"哇屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"178f3ee8bd6bf637b0853a79b98b0ac3f9717303","tid":2116904,"uid":76680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T12:42:50.000Z","msg":"咩公司"},{"pid":"5a465767044a70938425173dcbc35a77a5502166","tid":2116904,"uid":128102,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T12:43:21.000Z","msg":"已辭職既同事不用夾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n即係都諗過下要夾啦cls"},{"pid":"7c3b2074212f54a9422bca8d27217416ed6c650b","tid":2116904,"uid":251239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T12:44:12.000Z","msg":"咁on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50592d16618dad5f445be630950984b6919217a0","tid":2116904,"uid":126731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy